name: Asus VivoBook S15 S510 Core i5 8th Gen

This laptop features hybrid storage designed for supercharged data transfer that combines the blistering data speed of an SSD and the massive capacity of an HDD. The ASUS Laptop features a 15.6-inch Full HD display panel with ultra-narrow 7.8mm NanoEdge bezels and an 80% screen-to-body ratio. This display has 178Â° wide-view technology.

name: Asus X441MA Celeron Dual Core 14
description: Asus X441MA laptop features an Intel Celeron dual-core N4000 processor and up to 2.60 GHz speed, 500GB HDD storage, 4GB RAM, 14 Inch HD antiglare display, and 60Hz anti-glare panel, and 1366 x 768 resolution.

name: Asus X570ZD Ryzen 5 Gaming Laptop
description: Asus X570ZD Ryzen 5 gaming laptop includes AMD Ryzen 5 2500U processor that provides 6MB cache and up to 3.6GHz speed. It also contains a 15.6 LED-backlit FHD at 60Hz and an anti-glare panel with a 45% NTSC display. Its Nvidia GTX 1050 4GB GDDR5 VRAM graphics makes it suitable for gaming.

name: HP Elite X2 1012 G2 Core i5 7th Gen
description: HP Elite x2 1012 G2 tablet includes a 12.3-inch ultra-slim touch display with a resolution of 2736 x 1824p, a 60 Hz refresh rate, and a maximum brightness of 450 nits. It comes with 16 GB of RAM, a 256GB SSD, and a fast Core i5 7th generation processor.

name: HP EliteBook X360 1030 G2 Core i7 7th Gen
description: HP EliteBook X360 1030 G2 has 512GB SSD storage and 16GB RAM. It has an Intel Core i7 7th generation CPU with Intel turbo boost technology, which can run at up to 3.9 GHz. It includes a 1920 x 1080p touchscreen with four embedded stereo speakers, a spill-resistant backlit keyboard, and one USB Type-C with a thunderbolt / one HDMI port.

name: HP Pavilion 15-eh1070wm Ryzen 7 Slim
description: The HP Pavilion 15-eh1070wm laptop features a 15-inch micro-edge display with 178-degree wide viewing angles and crisp visuals. This laptop combines Wi-Fi 6 and Bluetooth 5.0 so you get a smoother wireless experience with more stable connectivity and 3x faster file transfer speeds from Wi-Fi 5. It has a powerful AMD AMD Ryzen 7-5700U processor, 8GB RAM, 512GB SSD storage capacity.

name: Dell Latitude 7390 Core i5 8th Gen 8GB RAM
description: Dell Latitude 7390 has 8GB of DDR4 RAM and a 256GB SSD drive. It features a 13.3-inch HD display as well as a fingerprint security mechanism that rapidly unlocks the laptop when you touch the sensor. It has backlight support, allowing you to work in low-light situations.

name: Dell Latitude 7480 Core i7 7th Gen
description: Dell Latitude laptop has a premium material unibody design with a sleek and soft-touch paint, and an optional woven carbon fiber back that covers the body. It has 256GB SSD storage capacity, 8GB RAM, multi-gesture touchpad, headphone / microphone combo jack, 2 x USB 3.0 / USB 3.0 / LAN / HDMI interface.

name: Dell XPS 13 9365 2-in-1 Core i5 8th Gen
description: The Dell XPS 13 9365 2-in-1 is a laptop and tablet size that can be used separately, both flexible and usable. You can rotate the laptop up to 360 degrees as needed. This Dell XPS laptop features powered by an Intel Core i5 8th generation processor with a base clock of 1.6GHz. This Dell laptop has an 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac wireless LAN, which delivers the most dependable Wi-Fi connection. The chiclet backlit keyboard is strong, full-length, and ergonomically designed.
